author: pmouawad
msg: Bug 52280 - The menu item Options / Choose Language does not change all the displayed text to the new language
Issue is due to the fact that on a french computer, default locale is fr_FR , so as _en bundles are missing it stays in French. Would be the same for all non english computers.

author: minfrin
msg: mod_proxy: Make ap_proxy_retry_worker() into an optional function. Allows
and mod_lbmethod_heartbeat to be loaded without mod_proxy yet being present,
which happens when modules are loaded in alphabetical order.
